{"tid":1534851,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"和理非學生聽住：唔係運動員既同我企响度！","createTime":"2019-09-03T06:45:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-03T08:51:55.000Z","uid":153876,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"5228f479059e8f426c5e04bb5d71cd98a1abcaa0","tid":1534851,"uid":153876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T06:45:57.000Z","msg":"狗嘅性格係見有野走就追。掉頭走，佢可以懐疑你犯法所以制服你，順便用你黎發洩。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">大家好似忘記哂6月學習嘅查身份證搜身程序。</span><br />\n<br />\n除非你肯定自己好跑得，否則，企响度，用堅定嘅眼神，拎部電話出黎live。<br />\n<br />\n之後佢會問你做咩喺度，要求查你身份證，<span style=\"color: red;\">你必須拎張身分證出黎</span>，咁你可以撚下狗，<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\">唔好俾佢查住，慢慢拖時間等街坊或記者。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n佢一定會話你，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">知唔知自己犯緊法</span></span>，因為佢要有懷疑先可以搜你身，唔好俾班狗嚇親，狗吠係好恐怖，但聽慣咗就當唱歌。<br />\n<br />\n你可以笑笑口回答，呢條法例我熟喎，問隻狗講清楚啲，<span style=\"font-size: large;\">你越冷靜，佢越淆底</span>。你有時間可以搵人問清楚。或者直接俾佢搜袋。<br />\n<br />\n到搜身搜袋，佢一定要响你面前搜，你絕對有權及有需要影住自己嘅私人物品。除非你有gear又<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">冇合理解釋</span>，否則佢只可以兇住你咁放你走。<br />\n<br />\n既然完成程序，佢係唔可以即時再hold住你，係時候喇！<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">你嘅憤怒就可以爆發</span></span>，你反而可以追問佢有咩唔做得啦，叫佢睇住自己啲伙記啦，分化下佢地。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">記住，你冇犯法，警民合作，練下膽識，日後屌狗都可以屌大力啲！逃走，只係得個驚字。</span><br />\n<br />\n怕狗既，同我去各大狗公園聽下狗吠，玩下狗。<br />\n未犯過法嘅，自己去裁判法院旁聽下，交通，稅務果啲傳召，認識下法律程序，唔好咁細膽。<br />\n<br />\n認真心痛你地俾狗兇，俾狗蝦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8644a0081f78f248e7614c68e0dd3b11f274cf3","tid":1534851,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T06:46:03.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月7日 (六) 1PM<br />\n機場交通壓力測試 (重考)</strong></div><br />\n<br />\n香港市民：<br />\n✅ 以遊客身份入機場觀賞飛機升降 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 唔識路就坐多幾轉車 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 必需繳付車資乘坐黨鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其他國藉居民：<br />\n各有各做, 自由發揮 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nyixFQQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnyixFQQ.png&h=cc1f24a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月8日 (日) 2PM<br />\n香港人權與民主法案集會<br />\n美國駐港澳總領事館</strong></div><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2GKH20p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2GKH20p.png&h=6178433f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0e32f70de88622daa3790a57ff1a6f91e69593e0","tid":1534851,"uid":45007,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T06:56:17.000Z","msg":"舉高對手都對頭噴野<br />\n有邊個敢相信正常程序<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"579896590f6d7c66917f7419d1a6b811967e98a9","tid":1534851,"uid":108415,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T07:01:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9aTtZ95.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9aTtZ95.png&h=6ec979fa&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"204a9aa119ea0a2bb37675f536ab464612debde1","tid":1534851,"uid":153876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0e32f70de88622daa3790a57ff1a6f91e69593e0","tid":1534851,"uid":45007,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T06:56:17.000Z","msg":"舉高對手都對頭噴野<br />\n有邊個敢相信正常程序<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T07:20:29.000Z","msg":"舉咩手呀，對住狼狗投降？梗係俾狗咬<br />\n<br />\n冷冷靜靜，胸有成竹，班狗唔L知你咩料，佢就只有跟程序做"},{"pid":"d99aee08992095bd346e0db1d5f8b7ee41f41a58","tid":1534851,"uid":283738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T08:51:55.000Z","msg":"推爆佢<br />\n<br />\n琴晚成個LIVE都衰里個<br />\n今朝又係"}]}